text: Association Football Clubs Tubize, also known as AFC Tubize is a Belgian football club located in the city of Tubize. The club last promoted to the first division in 2008. The club was founded in 1990 as the result of a merger of two clubs, F.C. Tubize and Amis Réunis de Tubize.
